This directory contains Matlab code for the numerical examples in the following
paper:

Pavel Sakov and Laurent Bertino "Relation between two common localisation
methods for the EnKF", submitted to Computational Geosciences.

Figure # |   Command               | Output
-------------------------------------------------------
   1     | cl_example              | plot-cl.ps
   2     | la_example              | plot-la.ps
   3     | k                       | plot-k-r=1.ps
   3     | k (set r = 1e-4 at l.3) | plot-k-r=0.0001.ps
   4     | tsq                     | plot-tsq.ps
   5     | t                       | plot-t-r=1.ps
   5     | t (set r = 1e-2 at l.3) | plot-t-r=0.01.ps
   5     | t (set r = 1e-4 at l.3) | plot-t-r=0.0001.ps
   6     | tla                     | plot-tla-r=0.01.ps
   7     | spectrum                | plot-spectrum-r=0.01.ps
